kydra (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add package-specific icon extraction from deb packages
  * Implement intelligent icon caching system with thread-safe access
  * Add fallback mechanism to generic deb icon when specific icons unavailable
  * Support icon extraction from installed desktop files
  * Search for icons in system icon themes and common directories
  * Add singleton-based PackageIconExtractor class for efficient management
  * Modernize PackageModel and PackageDelegate for dynamic icon loading
  * Implement comprehensive error handling for icon extraction failures

 -- Jonathan Thomas <echidnaman@kubuntu.org>  Mon, 15 Nov 2025 19:30:00 +0100

kydra (0.9.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fixed settings dialog functionality for version columns
  * Added immediate feedback when toggling version column settings
  * Improved signal communication between settings dialog and main window
  * Added dedicated column visibility control methods
  * Fixed dependency installation issues with qapt and libkf5config5
  * Fixed icon theme installation in Debian package
  * Fixed settings persistence for column visibility

 -- Jonathan Thomas <echidnaman@kubuntu.org>  Mon, 15 Nov 2025 17:30:00 +0100

kydra (0.9.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of Kydra
  * Modern KDE/Qt UI built on Muon foundations
  * Improved repository control and filtering
  * Faster parallel operations and metadata caching
  * Refined dependency viewer with clearer tree layout
  * Enhanced integration with KDE technologies
  * Multi-headed architecture for fast search and operations
  * Breeze-styled interface with Plasma integration

